header.gameNote: New York Life ACC Tournament - Quarterfinal

videos.description: Keve Aluma feeds Justyn Mutts down low, and Mutts takes advantage of the porous defense with a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Aluma sets up Mutts for a Virginia Tech slam) 2021/03/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aluma sets up Mutts for a Virginia Tech slam

videos.description: Naheim Alleyne finds David N'Guessan open for an easy layup under the hoop for Virginia Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Alleyne passes out of a double-team for N'Guessan's layup) 2021/03/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alleyne passes out of a double-team for N'Guessan's layup

videos.description: Armando Bacot receives the ball down low while a Virginia Tech defender overextends, and Bacot makes them pay with a slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bacot rattles the rim for UNC) 2021/03/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bacot rattles the rim for UNC

videos.description: Virginia Tech forces a turnover and Tyrece Radford is the beneficiary as he dunks it down in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Radford gets ahead of the pack for a Hokies jam) 2021/03/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Radford gets ahead of the pack for a Hokies jam

videos.description: R.J. Davis pokes the ball away, then scores the high-arcing basket off the glass with a chance at a 3-point play.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Davis gets the UNC crowd going with a steal and and-1 bucket) 2021/03/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Davis gets the UNC crowd going with a steal and and-1 bucket

videos.description: Leaky Black and R.J. Davis sink huge treys late for the Tar Heels to push them past the Hokies.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Black, Davis hit big 3s late for UNC to bury Virginia Tech) 2021/03/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Black, Davis hit big 3s late for UNC to bury Virginia Tech
